                    <ThingDef ParentName="MPBFPM_BaseHumanMakeableGun" Name="Cogboi_Gun_GraserPistol_Bond" Abstract="True">
                        <label>persona gamma ray laser pistol</label>
                        <description>A high energy laser pistol, which draws energy from a cold fusion power cell and fires in the Gamma Ray frequency. The "graser" beam effortlessly slices completely through the target's armor, burning a narrow cavity straight through them. The gamma ray pistol does a bit more damage than its laser counterpart, but has much less stopping power.\n\nThis weapon has an onboard persona that can bond to only a single person. The wielder and intelligent weapon can synchronize their reflexes and attack with frightening speed, accuracy, and creativity. Once bonded to a wielder, the weapon's persona will refuse to be wielded by anyone else.</description>
